c: 35
v: 12
t: "Kananjalo azifani iilwandle ezimbini. Enye inamanzi amnandi okuselwa aze amanye abe mtyuwa nakrakra. Ukanti kuzo zombini (ezi lwandle) nifumana inyama nikhuphe izihombiso enizinxibayo, kananjalo niyazibona iinqanawa zicanda (amanzi) ukuze nifune iziBele zaKhe; khon’ ukuze nibe nombulelo"